                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "  Polarization asymmetry for longitudinal polarization",
                "  at resonance"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma-ray spectrometry methods were used",
                " whereby capture gamma-rays were recorded. Three",
                " different types of measurements were used for the",
                " determination of the asymmetry Al",
                "  1) Al was measured in a large solid angle.",
                "     The capture gamma-rays were counted by a multi-",
                "     channel-scaler against the neutron TOF which",
                "     determined the neutron energy.",
                "  2) The angular distribution of gamma-rays was",
                "     measured from which were extracted all parameters",
                "     making up Al. Thus Al was extracted"
              ]
            }
          ],
